 filled with its share of angst, provided much needed healing and offered the perfect, most lovely ending to a passionate journey that I am not likely to ever forget...\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003ca href=\"http://prettywordsbookblog.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003e\n  \u003cimg src=\"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1412050368i/11316768.jpg\" class=\"gr-hostedUserImg\" loading=\"lazy\"\u003e\n\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pages/Pretty-Words-Book-Blog/860331017317983\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003e\n  \u003cimg height='“40\"' width=\"150\" src=\"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1413062455i/11461733._SX540_.png\" class=\"gr-hostedUserImg\" loading=\"lazy\"\u003e\n\u003c/a\u003e","rating":4,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/4971692?shelf=read"},"taggings":[{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"historical-romance","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/4971692?shelf=historical-romance"}},{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"epic-profound","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/4971692?shelf=epic-profound"}},{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"powerful","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/4971692?shelf=powerful"}}],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/375442832"},"likeCount":47,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":28,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"User:3076674":{"id":3076674,"__typename":"User","legacyId":3076674,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1567809544i/3076674._UY200_CR3,0,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":114,"viewableName":"Mishelle LaBrash","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/3076674-mishe